cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on improving the generalization performance of deep convolutional neural networks using unlabeled data on supervised tasks with few labeled instances. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, since the paper specifically deals with deep learning and convolutional neural networks, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely categories.
